# Infrastructure Rules

## Docker services
- Qdrant: localhost:6333 (HTTP), localhost:6334 (gRPC)
- Redis: localhost:6379
- Unstructured: localhost:8000
- Always run docker compose ps before starting backend to confirm all healthy

## Ports
- FastAPI backend: localhost:8080
- React frontend (Vite): localhost:5173

## Environment variables
- All secrets and config in .env
- .env is never committed to git
- .env.example is committed with placeholder values only
- pydantic-settings loads all vars through core/config.py

## Required .env variables
OPENAI_API_KEY=
COHERE_API_KEY=
QDRANT_URL=http://localhost:6333
UNSTRUCTURED_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
UPLOAD_DIR=./uploads
ENVIRONMENT=development
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

## ARQ worker
- Runs as a separate process alongside FastAPI
- Start with: uv run arq workers.ingestion_worker.WorkerSettings
- Connects to Redis via REDIS_URL from config
- Must handle timeouts gracefully and mark jobs as failed on timeout
- Never run the worker inside the FastAPI process